{"tid":513933,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[嚇死寶寶] 細數這些年被嚇到的IU","createTime":"2017-12-30T05:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T04:47:47.000Z","uid":34643,"like":286,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"910366875e064d52261544c8908a556513c5b8f0","tid":513933,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"細數這些年，一個極度需要呵護的知恩寶寶，不是在被嚇的狀態就是在被嚇的路上，妹子到底是真的被嚇到還是在賣萌呢，連受驚都這麼可愛的人真的是沒誰了！<br />\n<br />\n公演時被突然靠近的飛蛾嚇到&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2016/08/05/0d13370859c251da4bcd444645513faa1470369060.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2016%2F08%2F05%2F0d13370859c251da4bcd444645513faa1470369060.gif&h=e4975b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公演時音響突然中斷被嚇到&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2016/08/05/1a88508ead82ed383b8d35bf1a35ed1c1470369070.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2016%2F08%2F05%2F1a88508ead82ed383b8d35bf1a35ed1c1470369070.gif&h=0787ca12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n演唱會時被粉絲突然扔花上來嚇到&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2016/08/05/12f4791f131cb224825fd6766ce4fcb81470369140.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2016%2F08%2F05%2F12f4791f131cb224825fd6766ce4fcb81470369140.gif&h=dfe78f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2016/08/05/5b1474c85aaec21a0347924804482f221470374697_watermark.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2016%2F08%2F05%2F5b1474c85aaec21a0347924804482f221470374697_watermark.jpg&h=dc55b51d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n演唱會時粉絲扔水樽扔到面被嚇到&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/EbRV_OyTOZZObgKI14o2_-mGarKh1NTQADHBr4iuIffJa5zna9qyZIRSxVSyJRnTSgNnG0PZ1XPTcZ82T-sFC2_alOsIxwZxAxY=w9999-h9999\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FEbRV_OyTOZZObgKI14o2_-mGarKh1NTQADHBr4iuIffJa5zna9qyZIRSxVSyJRnTSgNnG0PZ1XPTcZ82T-sFC2_alOsIxwZxAxY%3Dw9999-h9999&h=73f3c9e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公演唱著唱著被突然跑上來的痴漢嚇到&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2016/08/05/d7e560c9957713bc7e5695a74d73c8af1470369170.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2016%2F08%2F05%2Fd7e560c9957713bc7e5695a74d73c8af1470369170.gif&h=7ee64e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接受採訪時不小心掉了mic被嚇到&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2016/08/05/a6125b8bf1c86b9c7e25bed627ae9c2f1470369201.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2016%2F08%2F05%2Fa6125b8bf1c86b9c7e25bed627ae9c2f1470369201.gif&h=2aa047f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接受採訪時突然打雷嚇到&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2016/08/05/932c3638b4a8892afea7e976abe1b0fa1470369227.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2016%2F08%2F05%2F932c3638b4a8892afea7e976abe1b0fa1470369227.gif&h=3042f2b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簽名活動看到粉絲的手臂紋身是自己的肖像，驚訝地大喊為什麼&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"https://koreadispatch.cdnser.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2017-07-04_15-53-27.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkoreadispatch.cdnser.be%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F2017-07-04_15-53-27.gif&h=e666eb8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n訪談節目被玩具狗嚇到&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2016/08/05/7812536f7718430f542ade30187384761470374982.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2016%2F08%2F05%2F7812536f7718430f542ade30187384761470374982.gif&h=4ff0c7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n製作MV時被突然扇動翅膀的鴨子嚇到&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2016/08/05/256742a532548a80ec2eefd4099452c41470375007.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2016%2F08%2F05%2F256742a532548a80ec2eefd4099452c41470375007.gif&h=9b07d229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n演唱會上唱錯歌詞也能把自己嚇到&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2016/08/05/a24ee1b9de4bbe7f6ef4186c606879051470375076.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2016%2F08%2F05%2Fa24ee1b9de4bbe7f6ef4186c606879051470375076.gif&h=5432bf1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2c341e0bdf302e5d3c91bd11180e3632fafe5b9","tid":513933,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9d2e613c89f9e10624eced1da2173b1dbe6324","tid":513933,"uid":38172,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:39:32.000Z","msg":"戀愛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b452b49f5760d9b31bde10ebb81ba3aab59ea266","tid":513933,"uid":60286,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"可愛到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d920a046e2a1a9f661dff715fb31715a4c903988","tid":513933,"uid":51904,"like":109,"dislike":13,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:02:41.000Z","msg":"喺床上被中出時嚇到"},{"pid":"b7cb5493b579ab139ac5e65e6c1154da4ec4db07","tid":513933,"uid":75802,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:13:36.000Z","msg":"竟然無英雄豪傑瞓教比盧弘喆嚇果幕"},{"pid":"536f5072be60724174d8fc97cd9dc495dc1e7fc0","tid":513933,"uid":2059,"like":48,"dislike":6,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"d920a046e2a1a9f661dff715fb31715a4c903988","tid":513933,"uid":51904,"like":109,"dislike":13,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:02:41.000Z","msg":"喺床上被中出時嚇到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:17:25.000Z","msg":"含含下俾條仔口爆嚇倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fb24cb01f962bd9fc6c57